'''Wild Wood''' is mentioned in lore as an ancient forest where [[Elves|elf-children]] wondered at their first Dawn.<ref>{{TT|Uruk}}</ref>

If taken literally, the Wild Wood should refer to some woods near [[Cuiviénen]] and the [[Orocarni]].<ref>{{S|Captivity}}</ref><ref>{{HM|Guide}}, p. 427</ref><ref>{{HM|AME}}, p. 5</ref>
